{
  "id": "cdrive-cleanup",
  "title": "让 C 盘再深呼吸一次 · 20+4 步清理指南",
  "mode": "html",
  "html": "<section style=\"max-width:660px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 4px;color:#1A1715;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',sans-serif;line-height:1.8;background:#FEFCF7;\">\n\n<!-- ============ TOP · 引子 ============ -->\n\n<section style=\"padding:36px 4px 0;\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#2A2420;margin:0 0 14px 0;\">大家好，我是 C 盘清理专家小超。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#2A2420;margin:0 0 14px 0;\">不知道你有没有过这种时刻：开机看到 C 盘那条<strong style=\"color:#B94A3F;\">红线</strong>，点“释放空间”等了半天只缩回两个 G；卸软件又怕哪天要用，只能干看着。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#2A2420;margin:0 0 22px 0;\"><strong>真正吃盘的那些目录，Windows 一键清理根本不动</strong>。我这几年清了几百块盘，下面 24 条是压箱底的方法，按<strong style=\"color:#0E8F77;\">场景分组</strong>、从浅到深排好，每条都标了<strong style=\"color:#0E8F77;\">风险等级</strong>。动手前先看一眼，C 盘大概都被什么占着：</p>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ============ 静态 SVG · 谁在占你 C 盘（典型 256GB 用户） ============ -->\n\n<section style=\"margin:6px 0 32px;padding:22px 20px 20px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:12px;\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.28em;color:#7A6E63;margin:0 0 4px 0;font-weight:700;\">TYPICAL DISTRIBUTION</p>\n  <p style=\"font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:#1A1715;margin:0 0 18px 0;\">谁在占你的 C 盘？</p>\n\n  <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 600 240\" style=\"display:block;width:100%;height:auto;\">\n    <line x1=\"150\" y1=\"28\" x2=\"150\" y2=\"200\" stroke=\"#E6DFD2\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n    <line x1=\"540\" y1=\"28\" x2=\"540\" y2=\"200\" stroke=\"#F1ECDF\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-dasharray=\"3 4\"/>\n\n    <!-- 01 应用/游戏 35% -->\n    <text x=\"144\" y=\"50\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#1A1715\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\">应用 / 游戏</text>\n    <rect x=\"150\" y=\"38\" width=\"390\" height=\"18\" rx=\"3\" ry=\"3\" fill=\"#0E8F77\"/>\n    <text x=\"546\" y=\"51\" fill=\"#0E8F77\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">35%</text>\n\n    <!-- 02 Windows 本体 25% -->\n    <text x=\"144\" y=\"82\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#1A1715\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\">Windows 本体</text>\n    <rect x=\"150\" y=\"70\" width=\"278\" height=\"18\" rx=\"3\" ry=\"3\" fill=\"#2AB892\"/>\n    <text x=\"434\" y=\"83\" fill=\"#0E8F77\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">25%</text>\n\n    <!-- 03 微信 / QQ 缓存 18% -->\n    <text x=\"144\" y=\"114\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#1A1715\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\">微信 / QQ 缓存</text>\n    <rect x=\"150\" y=\"102\" width=\"200\" height=\"18\" rx=\"3\" ry=\"3\" fill=\"#59D4B0\"/>\n    <text x=\"356\" y=\"115\" fill=\"#0E8F77\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">18%</text>\n\n    <!-- 04 休眠 + 虚拟内存 12% -->\n    <text x=\"144\" y=\"146\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#1A1715\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\">休眠 + 分页文件</text>\n    <rect x=\"150\" y=\"134\" width=\"134\" height=\"18\" rx=\"3\" ry=\"3\" fill=\"#F3B823\"/>\n    <text x=\"290\" y=\"147\" fill=\"#A86A00\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">12%</text>\n\n    <!-- 05 临时 / 缓存 / 下载 10% -->\n    <text x=\"144\" y=\"178\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#1A1715\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"600\">临时 / 缓存 / 下载</text>\n    <rect x=\"150\" y=\"166\" width=\"112\" height=\"18\" rx=\"3\" ry=\"3\" fill=\"#F8D472\"/>\n    <text x=\"268\" y=\"179\" fill=\"#A86A00\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">10%</text>\n\n    <text x=\"150\" y=\"220\" fill=\"#7A6E63\" font-size=\"11\">基于 256GB SSD · Win11 · 办公类用户的平均抽样</text>\n  </svg>\n\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#7A6E63;margin:14px 0 0 0;line-height:1.8;\">\n    能\"快速清出 10GB+\"的是<strong style=\"color:#A86A00;\">橙黄那两条</strong>——休眠/虚拟内存/临时文件都是\"Windows 为了自己方便存的\"，删了无副作用。<br/>\n    真正难搞的是<strong style=\"color:#0E8F77;\">绿色那三条</strong>——应用、Windows 本体、微信缓存，得靠迁移或卸载。\n  </p>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ============ 过渡 · 引导下载 ============ -->\n\n<section style=\"padding:0 4px 8px;\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#2A2420;margin:0 0 14px 0;\">这些占比里，<strong style=\"color:#0E8F77;\">微信 / 浏览器缓存</strong>你自己动手就能清；但像<strong style=\"color:#0E8F77;\">组件商店、休眠文件、分页文件</strong>这种，碰错一步就蓝屏。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#2A2420;margin:0 0 22px 0;\">不想折腾的，下面这张卡里的 <strong>Windows 优化大师</strong> 是联想应用商店今年评的「最具价值应用」，一键替你搞定。</p>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ============ 顶部下载卡（吉祥物 + 文案 + CTA · 与底部同版式语言） ============ -->\n\n<section style=\"margin:28px 0 44px;padding:0;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:14px;box-shadow:0 2px 0 rgba(14,143,119,0.06),0 8px 24px rgba(42,36,32,0.04);overflow:hidden;\">\n  <section style=\"background:#F1ECDF;padding:20px 20px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #E6DFD2;\">\n    <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"width:88px;vertical-align:middle;padding-right:16px;\">\n          <img src=\"https://mbluostudio.com/imgbed/images/2026/04/24/1777017191424-e6b8c26b.png\" alt=\"Windows 优化大师吉祥物\" style=\"display:block;width:88px;height:88px;border-radius:20px;background:#C8E5EC;\"/>\n        </td>\n        <td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">\n          <p style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.28em;color:#0E8F77;margin:0 0 4px 0;font-weight:700;\">SPONSOR · 赞助</p>\n          <p style=\"font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.3;color:#1A1715;margin:0 0 2px 0;\">Windows 优化大师</p>\n          <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#7A6E63;margin:0;\">专注清理优化 · 轻巧无广告</p>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"padding:18px 20px 20px;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0 0 16px 0;line-height:1.85;\">\n      C 盘日均释放 <strong style=\"color:#0E8F77;\">50 GB</strong>&nbsp;·&nbsp;强力卸载 <strong style=\"color:#0E8F77;\">流氓软件</strong>&nbsp;·&nbsp;微信 QQ <strong style=\"color:#0E8F77;\">专清</strong>&nbsp;·&nbsp;零广告零捆绑\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0;\">\n      <span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:11px 22px;background:#F3B823;color:#1A1715;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;border-radius:8px;margin-right:10px;\">↓ 点此免费下载</span>\n      <span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:11px 16px;background:transparent;color:#0E8F77;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;border:1px solid #0E8F77;border-radius:8px;\">联想商店 · 4.8 分</span>\n    </p>\n  </section>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ============ 目录 ============ -->\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 44px;padding:20px 20px;background:#F4F0E8;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.25em;color:#7A6E63;margin:0 0 12px 0;font-weight:700;\">CONTENTS · 四组 + 2026 新增</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;line-height:2;\">\n    <strong style=\"color:#0E8F77;\">Ⅰ · 临时文件与基础清理</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;01–05<br/>\n    <strong style=\"color:#0E8F77;\">Ⅱ · 大文件夹的迁移</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;06, 18, 19, 20<br/>\n    <strong style=\"color:#0E8F77;\">Ⅲ · 系统内置清理工具</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;07–13<br/>\n    <strong style=\"color:#0E8F77;\">Ⅳ · 深度操作（风险偏高）</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;14–17<br/>\n    <strong style=\"color:#F3B823;\">Ⅴ · 2026 新方法</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;21–24\n  </p>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ========== Ⅰ · 临时与基础 ========== -->\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 36px;\">\n  <p style=\"font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:64px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;line-height:1;margin:0 0 -18px 0;opacity:0.18;\">Ⅰ</p>\n  <p style=\"font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#1A1715;margin:0 0 4px 0;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:-4px;width:22px;height:22px;margin-right:8px;\"><line x1=\"16\" y1=\"3\" x2=\"9\" y2=\"13\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M5 14 L12 14 L15 22 L8 22 Z\" fill=\"#0E8F77\" opacity=\"0.2\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><line x1=\"8\" y1=\"16\" x2=\"9.5\" y2=\"21.5\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"11.5\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"16\" x2=\"13.5\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/></svg>临时文件 & 基础清理</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#7A6E63;margin:0 0 20px 0;\">花 5 分钟就能见效的动作。所有风险等级：低。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;vertical-align:baseline;\">01</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">临时文件清理</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#E8F8F2;color:#0E8F77;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#0E8F77\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>低</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\"><code style=\"background:#F4F0E8;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px;color:#0E8F77;font-family:Consolas,monospace;\">Win + R</code> → 输入 <code style=\"background:#F4F0E8;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px;color:#0E8F77;font-family:Consolas,monospace;\">%TEMP%</code> → 回车 → <code style=\"background:#F4F0E8;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px;color:#0E8F77;font-family:Consolas,monospace;\">Ctrl + A</code> → <code style=\"background:#F4F0E8;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px;color:#0E8F77;font-family:Consolas,monospace;\">Shift + Delete</code>。被占用的跳过。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;\">02</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">关闭休眠 · 释放 hiberfil.sys</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#E8F8F2;color:#0E8F77;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#0E8F77\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>低</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0 0 4px 0;\">体积 ≈ 物理内存的 60%。日常不用休眠就关掉。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">管理员 cmd → <code style=\"background:#F4F0E8;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px;color:#0E8F77;font-family:Consolas,monospace;\">powercfg -h off</code>。恢复：<code style=\"background:#F4F0E8;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px;color:#0E8F77;font-family:Consolas,monospace;\">-h on</code>。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;\">03</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">虚拟内存 pagefile.sys 搬家</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#FFF4E0;color:#A86A00;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#A86A00\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#A86A00\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#A86A00\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>中</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">右键此电脑 → 属性 → 高级系统设置 → 性能「设置」→ 高级 → 虚拟内存「更改」。取消自动勾选，C 盘选「无分页文件」，D 盘选「自定义」按系统推荐值。重启生效。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;\">04</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">删除 windows.old</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#E8F8F2;color:#0E8F77;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#0E8F77\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>低</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">右键 C 盘 → 属性 → 磁盘清理 → 清理系统文件 → 勾「以前的 Windows 安装」。单次能省 <strong>20–30 GB</strong>。代价：失去回滚旧系统的能力。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;\">05</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">回收站清空 + 调整上限</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#E8F8F2;color:#0E8F77;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#0E8F77\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>低</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">右键回收站 → 属性 → 为每个分区设置自定义上限，激进派直接勾「移除文件后立即删除」。然后清空。</p>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ========== Ⅱ · 大文件夹迁移 ========== -->\n\n<section style=\"margin:36px 0 0;\">\n  <p style=\"font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:64px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;line-height:1;margin:0 0 -18px 0;opacity:0.18;\">Ⅱ</p>\n  <p style=\"font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#1A1715;margin:0 0 4px 0;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:-4px;width:22px;height:22px;margin-right:8px;\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"7\" width=\"8\" height=\"11\" fill=\"#0E8F77\" opacity=\"0.15\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" rx=\"1.5\"/><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"13\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"13\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M17 8 L22 13 L17 18\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>大文件夹的迁移</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#7A6E63;margin:0 0 20px 0;\">治本。把高频增长的文件夹整体换到 D 盘。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;\">06</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">桌面文件夹整体搬家</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#E8F8F2;color:#0E8F77;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#0E8F77\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>低</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">此电脑 → 左侧「桌面」右键属性 → 位置「移动」→ 指到 D 盘新建的「桌面」文件夹 → 是（迁移原文件）。从此桌面一切都在 D 盘。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;\">18</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">浏览器下载路径改 D 盘</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#E8F8F2;color:#0E8F77;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#0E8F77\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>低</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0 0 4px 0;\"><strong>Edge：</strong>右上角 ··· → 下载 → 设置 → 位置改 D 盘。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\"><strong>Chrome：</strong>右上角 ··· → 设置 → 下载内容 → 位置改 D 盘，顺手勾「下载前询问每个文件的保存位置」。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;\">19</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">微信文件目录迁移</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#E8F8F2;color:#0E8F77;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#0E8F77\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>低</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">C 盘第一杀手。PC 微信 → 左下角三横线 → 设置 → 文件管理 → 更改目录 → D 盘。弹窗询问迁移历史记录选\"是\"。几十 GB 瞬间清净。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;\">20</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">QQ 文件目录迁移</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#E8F8F2;color:#0E8F77;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#0E8F77\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>低</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">QQ 面板 → 左下角三横线 → 设置 → 文件管理 → 更改目录 → D 盘。同理。</p>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ========== Ⅲ · 系统内置 ========== -->\n\n<section style=\"margin:36px 0 0;\">\n  <p style=\"font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:64px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;line-height:1;margin:0 0 -18px 0;opacity:0.18;\">Ⅲ</p>\n  <p style=\"font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#1A1715;margin:0 0 4px 0;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:-4px;width:22px;height:22px;margin-right:8px;\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"3\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"6\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"18\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"21\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"6\" y2=\"12\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><line x1=\"18\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"12\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><line x1=\"5.5\" y1=\"5.5\" x2=\"7.6\" y2=\"7.6\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><line x1=\"16.4\" y1=\"16.4\" x2=\"18.5\" y2=\"18.5\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><line x1=\"5.5\" y1=\"18.5\" x2=\"7.6\" y2=\"16.4\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><line x1=\"16.4\" y1=\"7.6\" x2=\"18.5\" y2=\"5.5\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg>系统内置清理工具</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#7A6E63;margin:0 0 20px 0;\">Windows 自己就带的，不少人从没点开。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;\">07</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">存储感知（定时自动清）</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#E8F8F2;color:#0E8F77;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#0E8F77\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>低</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">设置 → 系统 → 存储 → 开「存储感知」→ 配置成每周或每月，设定回收站/下载夹保留多少天。同页下方「更改新内容的保存位置」把新应用/文档/视频默认装到 D 盘。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;\">08</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">磁盘清理（临时文件）</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#E8F8F2;color:#0E8F77;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#0E8F77\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>低</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">开始菜单搜「磁盘清理」→ 选 C 盘 → 清理系统文件 → 勾上：Windows 升级日志、Internet 临时文件、错误报告、DirectX 缓存、传递优化文件、设备驱动程序包、缩略图、以前的 Windows 安装。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;\">09</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">系统还原与卷影清理</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#FFF4E0;color:#A86A00;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#A86A00\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#A86A00\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#A86A00\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>中</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">磁盘清理 → 清理系统文件 → 切「其他选项」→ 系统还原和卷影「清理」→ 删除。代价：失去较早的系统快照。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;\">10</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">卸载大型应用和游戏</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#E8F8F2;color:#0E8F77;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#0E8F77\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>低</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">设置 → 应用 → 应用和功能 → 排序「大小」。能卸的卸，Steam 大游戏可用「移动安装文件夹」整库搬走。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;\">11</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">删除未使用的语言包</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#E8F8F2;color:#0E8F77;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#0E8F77\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>低</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">设置 → 时间和语言 → 语言 → 选不用的删除。单个 200–500 MB。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;\">12</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">删除离线地图</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#E8F8F2;color:#0E8F77;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#0E8F77\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>低</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">设置 → 应用 → 离线地图 → 删除所有地图。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;\">13</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">卸载可选功能</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#E8F8F2;color:#0E8F77;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#0E8F77\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>低</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">设置 → 应用 → 应用和功能 → 可选功能。Windows Media Player、传真、Math Recognizer、老 IE 之类多数人不用。</p>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ========== Ⅳ · 深度操作 ========== -->\n\n<section style=\"margin:36px 0 0;\">\n  <p style=\"font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:64px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;line-height:1;margin:0 0 -18px 0;opacity:0.18;\">Ⅳ</p>\n  <p style=\"font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#1A1715;margin:0 0 4px 0;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:-4px;width:22px;height:22px;margin-right:8px;\"><path d=\"M12 3 L22 21 L2 21 Z\" fill=\"#B4372D\" opacity=\"0.12\" stroke=\"#B4372D\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"15\" stroke=\"#B4372D\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"18\" r=\"0.9\" fill=\"#B4372D\"/></svg>深度操作</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#7A6E63;margin:0 0 20px 0;\">风险偏高，只建议小 SSD 救急时用。操作前请备份。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;\">14</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">NTFS 文件夹压缩</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#FEE9E6;color:#B4372D;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#B4372D\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#B4372D\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#B4372D\"/></svg>高</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">右键目标文件夹 → 属性 → 高级 → 勾「压缩内容以节省磁盘空间」→ 应用于子文件夹。SSD 影响小，机械盘别做。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;\">15</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">Compact OS 压缩系统本体</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#FEE9E6;color:#B4372D;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#B4372D\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#B4372D\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#B4372D\"/></svg>高</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">管理员 cmd → <code style=\"background:#F4F0E8;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px;color:#0E8F77;font-family:Consolas,monospace;\">compact.exe /compactOS:always</code>。回收约 2 GB。关闭：<code style=\"background:#F4F0E8;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px;color:#0E8F77;font-family:Consolas,monospace;\">:never</code>。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;\">16</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">重建搜索索引</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#FFF4E0;color:#A86A00;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#A86A00\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#A86A00\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#A86A00\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>中</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">索引数据库偶尔涨到几 GB。设置 → 搜索 → Windows 搜索 → 更多搜索索引器设置 → 高级 → 重建。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#0E8F77;\">17</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">禁用预留存储</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#FEE9E6;color:#B4372D;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#B4372D\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#B4372D\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#B4372D\"/></svg>高</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">管理员 PowerShell → <code style=\"background:#F4F0E8;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px;color:#0E8F77;font-family:Consolas,monospace;\">Set-WindowsReservedStorageState -State disabled</code>。~7 GB。下次功能更新后生效；会让大版本升级更容易出问题。</p>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ========== Ⅴ · 2026 新增 ========== -->\n\n<section style=\"margin:36px 0 0;\">\n  <p style=\"font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:64px;font-weight:700;color:#F3B823;line-height:1;margin:0 0 -18px 0;opacity:0.28;\">Ⅴ</p>\n  <p style=\"font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#1A1715;margin:0 0 4px 0;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:-4px;width:22px;height:22px;margin-right:8px;\"><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"3\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"8\" stroke=\"#F3B823\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"16\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"21\" stroke=\"#F3B823\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"8\" y2=\"12\" stroke=\"#F3B823\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><line x1=\"16\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"12\" stroke=\"#F3B823\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><line x1=\"5.2\" y1=\"5.2\" x2=\"8.4\" y2=\"8.4\" stroke=\"#F3B823\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.7\"/><line x1=\"15.6\" y1=\"15.6\" x2=\"18.8\" y2=\"18.8\" stroke=\"#F3B823\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.7\"/><line x1=\"5.2\" y1=\"18.8\" x2=\"8.4\" y2=\"15.6\" stroke=\"#F3B823\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.7\"/><line x1=\"15.6\" y1=\"8.4\" x2=\"18.8\" y2=\"5.2\" stroke=\"#F3B823\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.7\"/><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#F3B823\"/></svg>2026 新方法</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#7A6E63;margin:0 0 20px 0;\">Win11 22H2+ 带来的新清理面板，以及老 SSD 上必跑的 DISM。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFBEF;border:1px solid #F3B823;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#A86A00;\">21</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">DISM 清理 WinSxS 组件存储</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#FFF4E0;color:#A86A00;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#A86A00\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#A86A00\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#A86A00\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>中</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0 0 14px 0;\">WinSxS 是 Windows 的\"影子仓库\"，用久了能涨到 15 GB+，磁盘清理<strong>清不动</strong>，要靠 DISM。</p>\n\n  <!-- 终端窗口 SVG (静态，仿 Mac 风 + 管理员 cmd) -->\n  <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 560 220\" style=\"display:block;width:100%;height:auto;margin:0 0 14px 0;\">\n    <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"560\" height=\"220\" rx=\"10\" ry=\"10\" fill=\"#1E1E1E\"/>\n    <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"560\" height=\"34\" rx=\"10\" ry=\"10\" fill=\"#2B2B2B\"/>\n    <rect x=\"0\" y=\"24\" width=\"560\" height=\"10\" fill=\"#2B2B2B\"/>\n    <circle cx=\"18\" cy=\"17\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F57\"/>\n    <circle cx=\"38\" cy=\"17\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FEBC2E\"/>\n    <circle cx=\"58\" cy=\"17\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#28C840\"/>\n    <text x=\"280\" y=\"22\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#A6A6A6\" font-size=\"12\" font-family=\"Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace\">管理员: cmd · Windows 组件清理</text>\n    <text x=\"20\" y=\"64\" fill=\"#6FDB96\" font-size=\"13\" font-family=\"Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace\">C:\\Users\\you&gt;</text>\n    <text x=\"144\" y=\"64\" fill=\"#D4D4D4\" font-size=\"13\" font-family=\"Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace\">Dism /Online /Cleanup-Image /AnalyzeComponentStore</text>\n    <text x=\"20\" y=\"88\" fill=\"#7A7A7A\" font-size=\"12\" font-family=\"Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace\"># 先扫一下看能回收多少，不动数据</text>\n\n    <text x=\"20\" y=\"128\" fill=\"#6FDB96\" font-size=\"13\" font-family=\"Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace\">C:\\Users\\you&gt;</text>\n    <text x=\"144\" y=\"128\" fill=\"#D4D4D4\" font-size=\"13\" font-family=\"Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace\">Dism /Online /Cleanup-Image /StartComponentCleanup ^</text>\n    <text x=\"144\" y=\"148\" fill=\"#D4D4D4\" font-size=\"13\" font-family=\"Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace\">     /ResetBase</text>\n    <text x=\"20\" y=\"172\" fill=\"#7A7A7A\" font-size=\"12\" font-family=\"Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace\"># 实际清理，10–30 分钟，结束后包缩水 5–15 GB</text>\n\n    <text x=\"20\" y=\"202\" fill=\"#6FDB96\" font-size=\"13\" font-family=\"Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace\">C:\\Users\\you&gt; _</text>\n  </svg>\n\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#7A6E63;margin:0;line-height:1.7;\"><strong style=\"color:#A86A00;\">代价：</strong>清完后无法再卸载已打过的更新（副本被删）。稳定系统上没影响。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFBEF;border:1px solid #F3B823;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#A86A00;\">22</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">OneDrive「释放磁盘空间」</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#E8F8F2;color:#0E8F77;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#0E8F77\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>低</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">Win11 默认把文档/图片同步到 OneDrive。任务栏 OneDrive → 设置 → 同步和备份 → 高级 → 节省磁盘空间「释放」。所有云端文件变占位符，用到才下载。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFBEF;border:1px solid #F3B823;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#A86A00;\">23</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">可视化扫盘找\"隐藏肥肉\"</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#E8F8F2;color:#0E8F77;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#0E8F77\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>低</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">Windows 自带的清理认不出游戏缓存、<code style=\"background:#F4F0E8;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px;color:#0E8F77;font-family:Consolas,monospace;\">node_modules</code>、视频草稿这些。用 <strong>WizTree</strong>（秒扫）或 <strong>WinDirStat</strong>（树状图经典），5 分钟定位 Top 10 大户。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"margin:0 0 20px;padding:18px 18px;background:#FFFBEF;border:1px solid #F3B823;border-radius:10px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#A86A00;\">24</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size:17px;color:#1A1715;\">Win11 清理建议</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:#E8F8F2;color:#0E8F77;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 8\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;width:30px;height:8px;margin-right:5px;\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#0E8F77\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0E8F77\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>低</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0;\">设置 → 系统 → 存储 → 清理建议。系统主动挑出\"大于 128 MB、90 天没打开\"的文件让你一键处理，比自己翻更省心。</p>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ============ 底部下载卡 · 大图 + 干净版式 ============ -->\n\n<section style=\"margin:48px 0 28px;padding:0;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E6DFD2;border-radius:14px;box-shadow:0 2px 0 rgba(14,143,119,0.06),0 10px 36px rgba(42,36,32,0.06);overflow:hidden;\">\n  <img src=\"https://mbluostudio.com/imgbed/images/2026/04/24/1777017190921-74f87db1.jpg\" alt=\"Windows 优化大师 · 联想应用商店最具价值应用\" style=\"display:block;width:100%;height:auto;margin:0;\"/>\n\n  <section style=\"padding:28px 22px 22px;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.28em;color:#0E8F77;margin:0 0 10px 0;font-weight:700;\">做有用的软件</p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:26px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.3;color:#1A1715;margin:0 0 8px 0;\">手动清理太累？<br/>让大师替你做。</p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#7A6E63;margin:0 0 20px 0;\">一键全盘扫描 · 分类精准清理 · 零广告零捆绑 · 风险低不误删</p>\n\n    <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2A2420;margin:0 0 18px 0;line-height:2;\">\n      ✓&nbsp;&nbsp;全盘垃圾清理，日均释放 50 GB<br/>\n      ✓&nbsp;&nbsp;强力卸载流氓软件，日均 7 个<br/>\n      ✓&nbsp;&nbsp;弹窗自动拦截，日均 15 条<br/>\n      ✓&nbsp;&nbsp;微信/QQ 专清，支持按号按时间筛选\n    </p>\n\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px 0;\">\n      <span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:13px 28px;background:#F3B823;color:#1A1715;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;border-radius:8px;margin-right:8px;\">↓ 免费下载 · 绿色版</span>\n      <span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:13px 18px;color:#0E8F77;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;border:1px solid #0E8F77;border-radius:8px;\">联想商店 · 4.8 分</span>\n    </p>\n\n    <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A6E63;margin:14px 0 0 0;padding-top:14px;border-top:1px dashed #E6DFD2;\">官方认证：联想应用商店 / 华为应用市场 / 鸿蒙应用市场 · 支持 Windows 10/11 全版本</p>\n  </section>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ============ 落款 ============ -->\n\n<section style=\"padding:20px 4px 40px;border-top:1px solid #E6DFD2;margin-top:12px;\">\n  <p style=\"font-family:'Source Han Serif SC','Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',serif;font-size:14px;color:#7A6E63;margin:0 0 6px 0;font-style:italic;\">以上风险标注仅供参考，实际影响因系统版本而异。深度操作前请先备份重要文件。</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#9B9084;margin:0;letter-spacing:0.08em;\">评论区欢迎补漏&nbsp;·&nbsp;2026-04-24</p>\n</section>\n\n</section>\n",
